{"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Assert","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Util","Lean.Meta.Tactic.FVarSubst","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Intro","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Revert"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.lean#L95-L107","name":"Lean.Meta.assertHypotheses","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.html#Lean.Meta.assertHypotheses","doc":"Convert the given goal `Ctx |- target` into `Ctx, (hs[0].userName : hs[0].type) ... |-target`.\nIt assumes `hs[i].val` has type `hs[i].type`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.lean#L87-L90","name":"Lean.Meta.Hypothesis","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.html#Lean.Meta.Hypothesis","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.lean#L64-L85","name":"Lean.Meta.assertAfter","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.html#Lean.Meta.assertAfter","doc":"Convert the given goal `Ctx |- target` into a goal containing `(userName : type)` after the local declaration with if `fvarId`.\nIt assumes `val` has type `type`, and that `type` is well-formed after `fvarId`.\nNote that `val` does not need to be well-formed after `fvarId`. That is, it may contain variables that are defined after `fvarId`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.lean#L55-L58","name":"Lean.Meta.AssertAfterResult","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.html#Lean.Meta.AssertAfterResult","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.lean#L42-L53","name":"Lean.Meta.assertExt","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.html#Lean.Meta.assertExt","doc":"Convert the given goal `Ctx |- target` into `Ctx |- (hName : type) -> hName = val -> target`.\nIt assumes `val` has type `type` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.lean#L29-L37","name":"Lean.Meta.define","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.html#Lean.Meta.define","doc":"Convert the given goal `Ctx |- target` into `Ctx |- let name : type := val; target`.\nIt assumes `val` has type `type` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.lean#L16-L24","name":"Lean.Meta.assert","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Assert.html#Lean.Meta.assert","doc":"Convert the given goal `Ctx |- target` into `Ctx |- type -> target`.\nIt assumes `val` has type `type` "}]}